Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.68,0:00:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.38,0:01:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm going to climax!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Shiori?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't raise your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:01:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is that really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said she got a serious fever and had to be hospitalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.73,0:02:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you find that strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean she didn't even have a cold to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, but that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why won't they tell us where she's hospitalized?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.33,0:02:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They told us we don't need to go see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the teachers are acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...telling us to study by ourselves and they're holding staff meetings all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm certain that something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you just assume...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that Shiori got raped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't want to believe it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they say there's no smoke without fire, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt would be terrible if it were true...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l will never accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's just a rumor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we have to investigate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lnvestigate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's up to the school and the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you, Mia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:03:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf there really is a rapist on the loose...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then we should find him and punish him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punish him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By using your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get back at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's just not fair to Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People's thoughts are much stronger than you can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's scarier than a spirit that wanders around after death in regret...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the heart of a living human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you shouldn't be thoughtless and talk about getting revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about what l said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's just that l remembered what happened at my previous school...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At your previous school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l'll tell you about it someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But keep this in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's nice and pretty, it can become cold and ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what a human heart is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.05,0:04:10.49,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,lnterview with the Teachers (3)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:12.06,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,This time around, we'll interview Assistant Principal Yasaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:13.92,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,''Students are my treasure''
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean your students are your treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's all talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still not satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over the rape, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We discussed this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.54,0:04:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it were true, it's just wrong to print the article.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not nice to Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know, but... it just feels weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard rumors that it might be one of our students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just saying that for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if it were true?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy would be coming to school pretending to be innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf we don't do anything right now, then he just might do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you want to be exposed to public ridicule?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones on the losing end all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls anybody there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing this, right, Ayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop playing these games...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's hiding somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where would he hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how come we don't see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard that the girls for the school newspaper were attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know. l know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayaka and Midori, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard Shiori from class A was raped by the same guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls the rapist from one of our classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:11.12,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Study Time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rapist just disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an eyewitness too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard it from a guy on the baseball team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sure it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow-up report on the rapist who disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard something really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earthbound spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a male student who hung himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the student council room several years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you think this earthbound spirit is the rapist who disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's worth checking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:53.64,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Student Council Room
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Mia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't feel any spiritual energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf this earthbound spirit is possessing the school...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then maybe he's wandering around the school grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we don't have to get the results in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These spirits love the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just wait till it gets dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were there any incidents like this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like people witnessing ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've never heard of any...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l haven't heard of any rumors like that at all either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sounds kind of fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean if you think about it, it's kind of odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that a spirit of a student who committed suicide several years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would start acting up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't find any spiritual energy in the area...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l'm kind of happy about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess it was just a rumor after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's starting to get a bit chilly in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf there's a strange phenomenon, they say that the temperature drops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin, hyo, tou, sha, kai, jin, retsu, zai, zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.11,0:11:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was one powerful spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with Reina's contacts, we can't find out where Shiori's hospitalized...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiori is a classmate of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So l thought we could get more details about the attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess we'll just have to keep taking risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to ask the two girls of the school newspaper that were attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought you were going to the club...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, the chief is in the student council room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he like this place so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This undulation...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the guy in the middle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Kitagawa. The student council head...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean the former head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Former?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:13:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitagawa stopped coming to school all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he stayed home all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as a result, he was no longer the head of the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he stop coming to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l really don't know why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not like he was being bullied...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was always getting good grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want any more people to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please tell us the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm telling you l don't have anything to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he reminded you of someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am l right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm really scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you to trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitagawa is responsible?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that wasn't Kitagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt didn't look human at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was definitely a spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitagawa's doppelganger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doppelganger?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls there anyone that knew Kitagawa very well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimizu might know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyu Shimizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was the vice-chair of the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, l think she was going out with Kitagawa at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know if we were going out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l met Kitagawa three years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l confessed to him three years ago on Christmas eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right where we stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitagawa said he liked me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, we never even kissed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you were going out for three years?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two went out on dates, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l even went over to his place one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't even hold my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess he was a late bloomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a girl like Shimizu in front of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:15:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was starting to feel uneasy as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then on the last day of the second semester...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l told him l wanted to break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.15,0:16:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l didn't really want to break up with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess l wanted to know how he felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf he was a late bloomer, then l wanted him to be more outgoing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You broke up with him in the student council room?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why the spirit likes that place...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitagawa thought he was really dumped by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He stopped coming to school, so l stopped by his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he wouldn't come out of his room...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess he was really suffering from a broken heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not that easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm guessing Kitagawa had sexual desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than the average person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he couldn't even touch the girl he loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he felt hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she wanted to break up with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt would've been good if he just withdrew into his own shell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was hopeless and full of regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And those feelings came out in a distorted shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't satisfy his sexual desires...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that became his doppelganger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's scary is the heart of a living human being...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard about the rapist who disappeared, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitagawa's doppelganger is responsible for all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyu, l'll get right to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still like Kitagawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.46,0:18:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can make the doppelganger disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to let Kitagawa satisfy his desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take good care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll get Kitagawa out of his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open this door, Kitagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's me, Kitagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kitagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's his mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'll stay at some busines hotel with her husband tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:19:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we have to make him open the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open this door, Kitagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wasn't going to break up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you listen to what l have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought l heard Mia's scream...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.73,0:21:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumi, Shimizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.77,0:22:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.91,0:22:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.94,0:22:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:22:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.65,0:22:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:23:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry for saying we should break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l really didn't mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.42,0:23:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l still like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.26,0:23:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.56,0:23:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please wake up! Please Kitagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.69,0:23:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin, hyo, tou, sha, kai, jin, retsu, zai, zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.63,0:23:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kitagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.17,0:23:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.84,0:23:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snap out of it, Kitagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.54,0:23:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitagawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.22,0:24:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyu...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.66,0:24:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're back, Kitagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know who l am, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.40,0:24:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.34,0:24:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we'll just leave the rest to Shimizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.44,0:24:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.07,0:24:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.34,0:24:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil spirit, disperse!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.21,0:24:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaman!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.86,0:24:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Kitagawa was able to satisfy his desires...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.76,0:24:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.83,0:24:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.90,0:24:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.31,0:25:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.48,0:25:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitagawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.59,0:25:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.50,0:25:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.56,0:25:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.60,0:25:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Keep going...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.45,0:25:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.10,0:26:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.11,0:26:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt felt good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.41,0:26:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.78,0:26:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.61,0:26:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.08,0:26:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitagawa and Shimizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.02,0:26:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're madly in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.85,0:26:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.29,0:26:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want a boyfriend too!